    "patch_code": "public static int formatlong\n    final long value, maxAs Octal Char, max As Binary char, negative, result;\n\n    maxAs Octal Char = value >> 4 & 1 ? maxAs Octal char : maxAs Octal char + 1;\n    maxAs Binary char = value >> 3 & 1 ? maxAs Binary char : maxAs Binary char + 1;\n\n    if (! negative && value < maxAs Octal char) {\n        return formatlong as Octal char;\n    }\n    if (! negative && value < maxAs Binary char) {\n        format long as Binary char;\n        return result;\n    }\n\n    if (length < maxAs Binary char) {\n        format long as Binary char;\n        return result;\n    }\n    format long as big int Binary char;\n    return result;\n}",
